# CIFAKE Reproduction Log

The CIFAKE LeNet baseline was reproduced locally.

## Setup
- Environment: Conda, Python 3.10
- Framework: TensorFlow/Keras
- Dataset: CIFAKE from Kaggle

## Results
- FAKE LeNet run completed successfully.
- REAL LeNet run completed successfully.
- FAKE validation accuracy reached approximately 79%.
- REAL validation accuracy reached approximately 56%.

## Notes
Some compatibility adjustments were required because the original implementation used older Keras arguments.
